{
  "stem": "26276.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You just lived from day to day like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, the whistle would blow at 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody had to jump off from the bunks, get dressed fast, go outside, be counted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they ship you over towards the kitchen window, with the little [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] tin cup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave us soup in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It felt like it was old dishwater from the Germans maybe, that they washed their dishes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the breakfast-- with a half inch slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said at that time that was made out of sawdust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the food to go out to work for the whole day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the evening, when we got back, again lined up, counted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once in a while, somebody would not to go back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He would hide, either wherever he was working so he could escape, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if they counted us and if there was somebody missing, they would call up every 10th man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every 10th, call him out from the lines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And either they would hang him, or otherwise we would have to wait, even if it took all night, until the dogs of the Germans or somebody brought him back, dead or alive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a lot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially in a camp by the name of Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the worst camp that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think about a year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About a year.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And why were you moved from Flossenburg to Gross-Rosen?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just picked a certain amount, whatever they needed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How many, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was even worse than all the other camps so far that I went to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we walked into that camp, they had mud right up to your chest, all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
